How can I deploy in a website so anyone can play it?

To deploy your game so anyone can play it, simply click the Publish button (top right on desktop, or bottom-right in Preview mode on mobile). This will give you a live URL that you can share with anyone!

Once published, you'll get a URL like yourproject.lovable.app that works on all devices. You can also connect a custom domain (like mygame.com) in Project Settings ‚Üí Domains if you have a paid plan.
